latestIgtvVideos.title: How I hydrate my skin with @honest_beauty ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I recently joined @honest_beauty seven sleeps to glower skin challenge and incorporated the "Beauty sleep resurfacing serum" to my skin care routine. I have been testing this out for 7 sleeps now & so far I love it! My skin instantly feels softer the next day. It is so good to my skin by gently resurfacing & hydrating, all while I sleep. It contains 5 AHA's (glycolic, lactic, citric, malic, and tartaric) plus 2 types of Hyaluronic acid which are amazing ingredients to have in your skin care routine. #honestambassador #sevensleeps Use my discount code "Dannaed" for free shipping on purchases containing one or more Honest Beauty products.
